label: F-Pnm Français 15123 (Pixérécourt Chansonnier)

metadata.label: Repository
metadata.value: Bibliothèque nationale de France, Département des Manuscrits

description: Copied by a single scribe. Many texts corrupt. Copied in Florence. Later owned by the librettist and collector René-Charles Guilbert de Pixérécourt (1773-1844); passed to Bibliothèque Nationale following Pixérécourt's death.
